# Developer Portfolio Project Overview

This is a premium, minimal, and modern developer portfolio built with Next.js 15, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS. The project follows the specifications outlined in [prd.md](mdc:prd.md).

## Project Goals
- Establish professional personal brand
- Showcase work history and projects
- Provide clear contact options
- Demonstrate design taste and coding ability
- Enable easy content management via MDX

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 15 with App Router
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4
- **Content**: MDX with Contentlayer
- **Animations**: Framer Motion
- **Theming**: next-themes (dark mode by default)
- **UI Components**: Lucide React icons, class-variance-authority, clsx

## Key Dependencies
- `contentlayer` - MDX content management
- `framer-motion` - Smooth animations and transitions
- `next-themes` - Dark/light mode toggle
- `rehype-*` & `remark-*` - MDX processing plugins

## Project Structure
- `src/app/` - Next.js App Router pages and layouts
- `content/` - MDX content files (to be created)
- `public/` - Static assets and images
- `components/` - Reusable React components (to be created)
- `lib/` - Utility functions and configurations (to be created)

## Design Principles
- Premium, minimal, modern aesthetic
- Dark mode by default with toggle option
- Smooth animations and micro-interactions
- Responsive design with mobile-first approach
- Performance-focused (Lighthouse 90+ target)
